column2: plot.sponge.before <- ggplot(sponge.before.df, aes(x = value, fill = batch)) + geom_density(alpha = 0.5) + scale_fill_manual(values=color.mixo(1:10)) + labs(title = 'OTU9 - before (Sponge)',x='Value',fill = 'Gel (batch)') + theme_bw() + theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust=0.5), panel.grid = element_blank())
